span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">定制便携包</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h4 style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">物流规格</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"></span></b></h4><p>	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">摄像头</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>尺寸：</span>27*102*27mm</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>重量：</span>63g</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">线夹</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>尺寸：</span>63*36*19mm</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>重量：</span>44g</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>线缆长度：</span>2.2m</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>重量</span>: 63g</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>