https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_08.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_09.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_10.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_11.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_12.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_13.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_14.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_15.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_16.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_17.jpg\"><img src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/Images/ProductImages/logitech/Spotlight/Spotlight_18.jpg\"><img name=\"SelectImage\" src=\"https://images.wincheers.net/UpLoad/Web/ProductImg/2019-03-14/NEW_XM/780.jpg\">', '<h4 style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">技术规格</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"></span></b></h4><p>	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>传感器技术：使用</span> Invensense 3D 技术的加速感应器和陀螺仪</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">空中鼠标：通过手势移动光标，像普通鼠标一样点击</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>按键数：</span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>电池：锂聚合物电池（</span>85 毫安）</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>电池寿命（可充电）：满电状态下最长</span> 3 个月使用时间，充电 1 分钟可进行 3 小时演示，1 小时即可充满</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>充电端口：机身为</span> USB-C 端口，通过随附的 USB-A 至 USB-C 线缆（13 厘米）充电</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>无线操作距离：最远</span> 30 米</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>预期按键寿命：</span>1 百万次点击</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>材质：</span><span>阳极氧化铝机身和塑料部件</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>连接性：罗技</span> 2.4 Ghz USB-A 接收器，低能耗蓝牙</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\">触觉反馈引擎：电量状态，距离提示，时间管理提醒</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"><br></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>跌落测试：</span>1 米跌落无碍</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span>选配备件：接收器</span><span>充电线缆</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:0.0000pt;text-indent:0.0000pt;\">	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p><h4>	<b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">产品规格</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"></span></b></h4><p>	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#666666;font-size:10.5000pt;\"><span>尺寸（</span>mm）：131.3 * 28.1&nbsp;* 12.1（高